metadata.name: 8-bit NPCs #2
metadata.description: 8-bit NPCs are a collection of 699 8 bit computed NFTS that instantly reveal roaming around the Ethereum blockchain. By holding an 8-bit in your wallet you gain the rights to its IP. That means you the owner, will be able to use your 8-bit NPC in any of your graphic design ventures. Each 8-bit NPC comes with their own build file, This means you will be able to customize your 8-bit any way you desire.
